<h2><a name='sect0' href='#toc0'>Name</a></h2>
<p>
MPI_Status_f082f, <a href="../man3/MPI_Status_c2f08.3.php">MPI_Status_c2f08</a> - Translates a Fortran 2008 status
into a Fortran INTEGER-style status, or vice versa.
